    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "Ordering a Main Dish",
          "arabic": "طلب طبق رئيسي"
        },
        "text": "To order, you can use 'Bghit...' (I want...) followed by the name of the dish. For example, 'Bghit ṭajin d-dajaj' (I want chicken tagine). If ordering for multiple people, you might say 'Jūj ṭajin d-l-ḥam' (Two meat tagines).",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "بغيت طاجين الدجاج.",
            "english": "I want chicken tagine.",
            "transliteration": "Bghit ṭajin d-dajaj."
          },
          {
            "arabic": "جوج طاجين اللحم عافاك.",
            "english": "Two meat tagines, please.",
            "transliteration": "Jūj ṭajin l-lḥam 3afak."
          }
        ],
        "audioText": "بغيت طاجين الدجاج. جوج طاجين اللحم عافاك."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "Asking About Ingredients",
          "arabic": "السؤال عن المكونات"
        },
        "text": "If you have allergies or just want to know what's in a dish, you can ask 'Ach fih...?' (What does... contain?) or 'Wash fih...?' (Does it contain...?). For example, 'Ach fih had ṭajin?' (What does this tagine contain?)",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "أش فيه هاد الطاجين؟",
            "english": "What does this tagine contain?",
            "transliteration": "Ach fih had ṭajin?"
          },
          {
            "arabic": "واش فيه البصل؟",
            "english": "Does it contain onion?",
            "transliteration": "Wash fih l-bṣal?"
          }
        ],
        "audioText": "أش فيه هاد الطاجين؟ واش فيه البصل؟"
      }
    },
