            "transliteration": "Wash 3andkom baṭaṭa mqlīya?"
          }
        ],
        "audioText": "بغيت شلاضة مغربية. واش عندكم بطاطا مقلية؟"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "Special Requests",
          "arabic": "طلبات خاصة"
        },
        "text": "For special requests, you can use 'Mūmkin...?' (Is it possible...?) or 'Bghit... bla...' (I want... without...). For example, 'Mūmkin bla ḥār?' (Is it possible without chili/spicy?).",
